lead_paragraph: England striker Harry Kane says he is ready to face Scotland in a World Cup qualifier on Friday despite having played only 70 minutes of football since injuring his ankle seven weeks ago.

headline.print_headline: Kane Able to Face Scotland Despite Lack of Football
